 Slash 对 Guns N' Roses 的《Sweet Child Of Mine》的吉他前奏最初是为了“摆脱这首歌”而写的https://www.nme.com/news/music/slashs-guitar-intro-to-guns-n-roses-sweet-child-of-mine-was-originally-writing-to-get-rid-of- the-song-3580152?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=slashs-guitar-intro-guns-n-roses-sweet-child-of-mine-最初是为了摆脱-而写的歌曲Alex RigottiWed, 31 Jan 2024 20:54:08 +0000 Music NewsNewsRockhttps://www.nme.com/?p=3580152 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/2024-Slash-Guns-Roses.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="斜线（摄影：Shlomi Pinto/Redferns）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/2024-Slash-Guns-Roses.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/2024-Slash-Guns-Roses-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/2024-Slash-Guns-Roses-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/2024-Slash-Guns-Roses-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/2024-Slash-Guns-Roses-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/2024-Slash-Guns-Roses-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “好吧，让我们尝试以某种方式完成这项工作”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/slashs-guitar-intro-to-guns-n-roses-sweet-child-of-mine-was-originally-written-to-get-rid-of-the-song-3580152">Slash 对 Guns N&#39; Roses 的《Sweet Child Of Mine》的吉他前奏最初是为了“摆脱这首歌”而写的，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/2024-Slash-Guns-Roses.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="斜线（摄影：Shlomi Pinto/Redferns）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/2024-Slash-Guns-Roses.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/2024-Slash-Guns-Roses-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/2024-Slash-Guns-Roses-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/2024-Slash-Guns-Roses-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/2024-Slash-Guns-Roses-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/2024-Slash-Guns-Roses-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/guns-n-roses">Guns N&#39; Roses</a>贝斯手 Duff McKagan 透露， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/slash">Slash</a>为《Sweet Child Of Mine》创作的标志性吉他前奏是为了“摆脱”这首歌而写的。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/film-interviews/slash-glastonbury-guns-n-roses-horror-movie-the-breach-3463459">Slash 谈论格拉斯顿伯里音乐节、枪炮玫瑰乐队和血腥的新恐怖电影《The Breach》</a></strong></li></ul><p>在<em>Songcraft</em>播客的最新一集中，麦卡根表示，Slash 写引子是一种破坏行为，他“不喜欢”当时的吉他手伊兹·斯特拉德林 (Izzy Stradlin) 向他呈现的和弦。</p><p> “伊兹掌握了三个和弦，”麦卡根回忆道。 “好吧，那是……‘你用它做什么？’ Axl 很喜欢它：“好吧，让我们尝试以某种方式完成这项工作。”在《Sweet Child o&#39; Mine》的介绍中，Slash 就是不喜欢 D、C、G 三个[和弦进行]。”然后他说 Slash 显然告诉他：“我们必须以某种方式摆脱这首歌。”</p><p>斯莱什随后写下了“这首扭曲的、无调性的东西”，但他毁掉这首歌的努力仍然徒劳。 “当然，尝试摆脱这首歌的部分完全成功了，”麦卡根说。 “这是这首歌的精彩介绍，突然间我们有了这首民谣。 ......这只是表明当时乐队的一切都很顺利。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Guns N&#39; Roses - Sweet Child O&#39; Mine（官方音乐视频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/1w7OgIMMRc4?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe title="Spotify 嵌入：EP。 223 - 枪炮队的达夫·麦卡根玫瑰（“内战”）" style="border-radius: 12px" width="100%" height="152" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen allow="autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; fullscreen; picture-in-picture" loading="lazy" src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/episode/2YVKhsBAFaxkaNfoaByBvh?utm_source=oembed"></iframe></p><p>麦卡根最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/duff-mckagan-defends-guns-n-roses-playing-three-and-a-half-hour-sets-3560541">为乐队演奏了三个半小时的冗长曲目进行了辩护</a>，他说：“别误会我的意思——如果我们只演奏两个半小时，我的身体会喜欢的。大多数乐队都会演奏两个小时。两个小时十分钟左右，我们要玩三个[小时]三十[分钟]。我希望打得短一些，因为这样第二天我的疼痛就会减轻一些。</p><p> “但是，歌曲太多了，人们会一直听下去。没有人离开，所以这就像是，“好吧，他们一定很享受这个。”我们会推出‘Coma’或‘Locomotive’。”</p><p>在其他新闻中，Slash <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-slash-play-guns-n-roses-use-your-illusion-deep-cut-live-for-the-first-time-3578139">有史以来第一次演奏了 Guns N&#39; Roses 的深度剪辑</a>。他为墨西哥的歌迷带来了 1991 年专辑“Use Your Illusion I”中的“Don&#39;t Damn Me”的惊喜表演。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/slashs-guitar-intro-to-guns-n-roses-sweet-child-of-mine-was-originally-written-to-get-rid-of-the-song-3580152">Slash 对 Guns N&#39; Roses 的《Sweet Child Of Mine》的吉他前奏最初是为了“摆脱这首歌”而写的，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
